to them in about a week.

01:19:11.331 --> 01:19:14.635 position:13% line:83% align:start
I see. Well, how much of it
do you still have left to cut?

01:19:14.668 --> 01:19:17.371 position:7% line:89% align:start
Uh, about three hours, I think.

01:19:17.404 --> 01:19:20.107 position:13% line:83% align:start
That much? Will you be able
to finish in time?

01:19:20.140 --> 01:19:23.377 position:10% line:83% align:start
I mean, I have a whole week,
so probab...

01:19:23.410 --> 01:19:25.212 position:33% line:89% align:start
(stammering)

01:19:25.245 --> 01:19:26.647 position:44% line:89% align:start
Aah!

01:19:29.182 --> 01:19:30.317 position:24% line:89% align:start
(whimpers, grunts)

01:19:30.350 --> 01:19:31.184 position:41% line:89% align:start
(gasps)

01:19:32.619 --> 01:19:34.087 position:35% line:89% align:start
Miss Pompo.

01:19:34.121 --> 01:19:35.289 position:41% line:83% align:start
POMPO:
How's our Gene doing?

01:19:36.490 --> 01:19:38.091 position:38% line:5% align:start
 <i>MYSTIA:</i>
 <i>He's sleeping.</i>

01:19:38.125 --> 01:19:39.326 position:35% line:89% align:start
He's fine.

01:19:39.359 --> 01:19:40.862 position:13% line:89% align:start
They think it's just anemia

01:19:40.895 --> 01:19:42.663 position:27% line:83% align:start
and say he should
recover after some rest.

01:19:42.696 --> 01:19:44.097 position:33% line:89% align:start
That means...

01:19:44.131 --> 01:19:46.266 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yep. From overwork.

01:19:46.533 --> 01:19:49.169 position:30% line:83% align:start
One more thing.
The doctor insists

01:19:49.202 --> 01:19:50.604 position:30% line:83% align:start
that he's going
to need to stay in bed

01:19:50.637 --> 01:19:52.339 position:16% line:89% align:start
till the end of the week.

01:19:52.372 --> 01:19:53.540 position:21% line:89% align:start
If that's the case...

01:19:57.778 --> 01:19:59.881 position:41% line:83% align:start
 <i>POMPO:</i>
 <i>With Gene out of commission,</i>

01:19:59.914 --> 01:20:02.316 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll need to find someone else</i>
 <i>to finish editing.</i>

01:20:16.363 --> 01:20:19.666 position:21% line:83% align:start
