your movie, your edit.

01:20:27.240 --> 01:20:28.675 position:41% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

01:20:28.709 --> 01:20:31.545 position:10% line:89% align:start
I was looking forward to it.

01:20:40.354 --> 01:20:42.189 position:21% line:89% align:start
Gene, can I come in?

01:20:42.222 --> 01:20:43.858 position:35% line:89% align:start
