01:20:45.225 --> 01:20:47.227 position:30% line:89% align:start
(gasps, sighs)

01:20:47.260 --> 01:20:49.229 position:16% line:89% align:start
I thought you'd be here.

01:20:49.262 --> 01:20:51.565 position:13% line:89% align:start
Let's go back to hospital.

01:20:51.598 --> 01:20:54.334 position:38% line:83% align:start
