01:21:36.911 --> 01:21:39.814 position:13% line:83% align:start
But we're not going to be,
not anymore.

01:21:45.787 --> 01:21:47.822 position:5% line:89% align:start
 <i>The last thing I'll say is this.</i>

01:21:48.990 --> 01:21:52.225 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>Your music truly is wonderful.</i>

01:21:52.259 --> 01:21:54.896 position:24% line:89% align:start
However, that aria?

01:21:56.763 --> 01:22:00.434 position:7% line:89% align:start
