01:22:22.689 --> 01:22:24.591 position:21% line:89% align:start
and their money, too.

01:22:26.027 --> 01:22:29.763 position:33% line:83% align:start
That's why...
I refuse to give up.

01:22:31.999 --> 01:22:33.400 position:41% line:89% align:start
(sighs)

01:22:40.975 --> 01:22:42.642 position:41% line:89% align:start
Mmm...

01:22:42.676 --> 01:22:44.979 position:33% line:83% align:start
In that case,
I'm not leaving, either.

01:22:45.012 --> 01:22:46.513 position:44% line:89% align:start
