01:22:58.025 --> 01:22:58.960 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

01:23:03.697 --> 01:23:06.566 position:33% line:5% align:start
Unbelievable.
You two are something else.

01:23:20.347 --> 01:23:22.682 position:13% line:83% align:start
Oh, that's the first scene
I shot.

01:23:22.716 --> 01:23:24.618 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yeah. Sorry.

01:23:24.651 --> 01:23:27.521 position:19% line:83% align:start
But it's not necessary,
