01:25:27.707 --> 01:25:29.476 position:7% line:89% align:start
 <i>...in order not to give up...</i>

01:25:30.878 --> 01:25:32.079 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>I will cut!</i>

01:25:32.113 --> 01:25:33.848 position:10% line:89% align:start
